net.dv8tion.jda.client.managers

Class ApplicationManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.dv8tion.jda.client.managers.ApplicationManager

  • public class ApplicationManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Facade for an ApplicationManagerUpdatable instance.
    Simplifies managing flow for convenience.

    This decoration allows to modify a single field by automatically building an update RestAction

    Since:
    3.0
    Author:
    Aljoscha Grebe
